mrBBIO

mrBBIO is a Python module for using Arduino-like language to control IO 
pins on the BeagleBone. There's lots of work still to be done. See "Issues"
tab on Github for list of features to be implemented. Please feel free to
contribute bugfixes and implement features.

Some code based on PyBBIO by Alexander Hiam: 
https://github.com/alexanderhiam/PyBBIO
